Executive Profile
Ronald D. Truex  President and General Manager, Creighton Brothers, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships66--
Background

		Mr. Ronald D. Truex serves as the President and General Manager of Creighton Brothers Llc. Mr. Truex joined Creighton Brothers in 1970 in the sales department. He has served as the President of the Indiana State Poultry Association and the Indiana State Egg Board. He is also a former Chairman of the American Egg Board. Mr. Truex has been an Independent Director of Lakeland Financial Corp. and its subsidiary Lake City Bank since October 2010. He serves on the Lakeland ... Regional Sewer District Board, the Kosciusko County Economic Development Board, the Kosciusko County Solid Waste Board and the Drainage Board. He is a Kosciusko County Commissioner. He serves on Kosciusko County Crime Stoppers board. Mr. Truex serves on the United Egg Producers Board of Directors. He is a past board member of the State Board of Animal Health.Read Full Background




